# NICONET
 
NICONET IS THE NETWORK OF FREE OFF WIRELESS GRID ROUTERS WHICH  WILL REPLACE THE CONSUMER INTERNET!

USE SOLAR TO CHARGE BATTERIES!

USE BIKE GENERATORS WITH TRASH-SOURCED MOTORS TO CHARGE BATTERIES!

GET VOLUNTEERS TO HOST BRIDGES FROM THE CENTRALIZED INTERNET TO NICONET!

ASK FOR DONATIONS OF HARDWARE, RUN CLINICS AT THE PUBLIC LIBRARY WHERE WE BRING TOGETHER THE COMMUNITY WHO WILL RUN THE NETWORK WITH HACKERS WHO CAN TAKE ALL DONATED HARDWARE AND TURN IT INTO MESH ROUTERS RUNNING [OPENWRT](https://openwrt.org/) WHICH ARE ALL OPEN AND FREE!

ALL ROUTERS AND POWER INFRASTRUCTURE WILL BE BUILT INTO ART INSTALLATIONS AND FASHION WITH A MAXIMALIST SOLARPUNK DESIGN AESTHETIC!

BUILD NODES INTO FASHION AND [TRASHCARTS](scrolls/TRASHCARTS)!


